name: Compare Owner Holiday Rentals
tag_list: vacation-rental-by-owner, vacation-rentals-by-owner, vacation-rentals, holiday-rentals, villa-rentals, holiday-rentals-by-owner
overview:
Provides advice for Vacation Rentals Owners on how amd where to advertise Vacation Rentals online.

Compare Owner Holiday Rentals (COHR) helps owners of vacation rentals accommodation make the right choices for advertising their vacation rentals on the internet. With so many portals, directories and listing sites for holiday rental owners to choose from, it can be confusing to determine where to advertise your vacation rental. Compare Owner Holiday Rentals provides comparisons and reviews of Vacation Rentals by Owner sites, including information on pricing, free trials and number of listings.

COHR also provides Special Offers and Discounts to many of the leading Vacation Rental by Owner sites.

In addition, COHR solicits comments from both vacation rentals owners and renters on their experience using a particular Vacation Rental by Owner website.
